Interface Calculate

All Known Implementing Classes:
Div, Equal, Less, LessEq, Member, Minus, More, MoreEq, Mult, NotEq, Plus, Power
public interface Calculate

This is the common interface for code calls in call terms. Each call term, when initialized, will have a pointer to an instance of a class that implements this interface.

Version:
1.0.3
Author:
Okhtay Ilghami, http://www.cs.umd.edu/~okhtay
